
/*
 * Reads the content from a specified stream node within the arguments, allowing you to process or manipulate the data from an open stream, such as one from an HTTP request. 
 * 
 * 1. [io.stream.read] - Reads data from the specified stream.
 * 2. [x:@.arguments/*/file/*/stream] - Specifies the location of the stream node within the arguments to read from.
 */
io.stream.read:x:@.arguments/*/file/*/stream
